= Overview =


The property commons is a network of [[Propertytrust]]s, governed democratically. The precise form of governance is agreed upon by the trustees of the networked republic of trusts and commons, but must honor the [[principles of organization]].

The economic arrangement the property commons creates, in conjunction with the other [[Vested Commons]], establishes the economic model of [[Utilicontributism]]. 


